sentence: One thing is certain: Trump will make the final decisions and will surely spend money to defeat Republicans like Liz Cheney who voted to impeach him following the Jan. 6, 2020 assault by his supporters on the U.S. Capitol, the sources said.
author: Jarrett Renshaw and Alexandra Ulmer
title: Exclusive-Trump Weighs How Deeply To Dig Into His War Chest For November Elections
